guibutton
Element


guibutton
&guibutton.purpose;


&guibutton.synopsis.gen;
Description



GUIButton identifies the text that appears on a
button in a graphical user interface.


Processing expectations


&format.inline; &pexp.moreinfo;




&guibutton.parents.gen;
&guibutton.children.gen;

Attributes

moreinfo



If MoreInfo is set to RefEntry,
it implies that a RefEntry exists which further describes the
GUIButton.





See Also
&guibutton.seealso.gen;

